{"tid":2249379,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地漢先後闖入劉鑾雄李澤楷大宅 欲攞錢兼求職 今判囚20個月","createTime":"2020-10-19T09:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T10:28:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f5884d0036be13215e965d5b174aef5478129377","tid":2249379,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:56:00.000Z","msg":"內地漢去年9月先後闖入華人置業前主席「大劉」劉鑾雄及電訊盈科主席「小小超」李澤楷名下大宅，聲稱要攞錢及求職，最終遭警方拘捕。他在警誡下聲稱知道大劉既富有又慷慨，更自揭曾四度來港，每次均尋訪富豪住宅，包括「賭王」何鴻燊四太梁安琪及女兒何超蓮、何超盈的住所。涉案內地漢今承認兩項企圖入屋犯法罪，法官念在他患有精神分裂症，而且案中沒有財物損失，判他入獄20個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/R2F3UXIIMVDWVHWDLVBSPHWSXY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FR2F3UXIIMVDWVHWDLVBSPHWSXY%2F&d=Ts2DrwFYYQI5JZ%2BOCIR9ZmLrBTEyyW%2B%2F%2BTJtsqEcrWg%3D&h=bbab3948\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201019%2FR2F3UXIIMVDWVHWDLVBSPHWSXY%2F&h=d9d65a4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201019/R2F3UXIIMVDWVHWDLVBSPHWSXY/</a>"},{"pid":"03da649aa236081a49c81e985e675edb7cbfae79","tid":2249379,"uid":6030,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:57:49.000Z","msg":"常山趙子龍？"},{"pid":"62ff0f0063434cb3af917bdc72323c500a21a6bd","tid":2249379,"uid":14103,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T09:59:04.000Z","msg":"嘩 邊位波台狗咁癲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c0ed1a99b8f0a183ef00fdace7f2d2e5ee5c00","tid":2249379,"uid":91833,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"入到去嘅就唔係黐線。。。"},{"pid":"a35da0382fd00212c18e502c6d79f8a65983149b","tid":2249379,"uid":335434,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"入屋爆格斷到正咁先判20個月 <br />\n依家幾個人帶支觀星筆同包索帶出街閒閒地都要坐兩年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2b1c6f5d518ccd93